summary:
### Summary of ASX Announcement (Appendix 3G - Westpac Banking Corporation):  

- **Security Issuance**: 22,977 unquoted **Share Rights (WBCAB)** issued under the **Equity Incentive Plan (EIP)** on **8 May 2025**.  
  - No key management personnel (KMP) involvement.  
  - Terms detailed in Westpac’s [2024 Annual Report (p.255)](https://www.westpac.com.au/content/dam/public/wbc/documents/pdf/aw/ic/wbc-annual-report-2024.pdf).  

- **Capital Structure Impact**:  
  - Total **unquoted Share Rights on issue**: 4,567,803 (WBCAB).  
  - No material dilution (issued under Listing Rule 7.2, using 15% placement capacity).  

- **No other material information** (e.g., trading impact, capital raising, or financial data).  

**Ruling**: Routine employee incentive issuance; negligible liquidity/valuation effect.
